' PlantUML — preview renders this to an image (needs the `plantuml` CLI: brew install plantuml).
@startuml
title Diagram preview flow

actor User
participant Editor
participant DiagramRenderer as R
participant "dot / plantuml" as CLI

User -> Editor : open .puml / .dot
Editor -> R : render(source)
R -> CLI : run
CLI --> R : PNG bytes
R --> Editor : image (cached by source hash)
note right of Editor : zoom re-fits the cached image
@enduml
